data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. PRICE ADJUSTMENT.....Welcome Home! This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home has been meticulously maintained.  The updates to the home include but are not limited to a newer roof 2021, AC 2019, Water Heater 2022, indoor laundry room, just to name a few.  The family room boasts a beautiful brick wood burning fireplace with mantle perfect for warming up on cool nights or just enjoying the glow of the fire after a long day.  The large screened in patio area is ideal to enjoy outdoor family activities. There is a concrete slab in the rear yard perfect for shooting hoops or outside games.  The rear yard is fully fenced.  There is a fire hydrant in the front yard, and the home is stones throw to a family park, with swings and tennis courts.  Other great characteristics is community is close to shopping, restaurants, medical facility, and a short distance to downtown Bartow where you will find many shops and activities to enjoy.
